@startuml
title Desktop — preparation pipeline before the simulation page (reference sequence)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 220

actor "Operator" as Op
participant "DatasetGenerationPage" as DGP
participant "SUMOConfigManager" as SCM
participant "RouteGenerationPage" as RGP
participant "NetworkParser" as NP
participant "SimulationView /\nAreaSelectionView" as SV
participant "SimulationPrepWorker" as SPW
participant "SimulationDBService" as DBS
database "SimulationDB\n(SQLite)" as SimDB
participant "MainWindow" as MW
participant "SimulationPage" as SimP

Op -> DGP : select / validate .sumocfg,\n browse referenced assets
DGP -> SCM : persist sumocfg path,\n list net/routes from XML

Op -> RGP : open **Define simulation**
RGP -> SCM : resolve network path from sumocfg
RGP -> NP : parse .net.xml
NP --> RGP : road / junction model
RGP -> SV : load_network(parser)
SV --> Op : SUMO map rendered

Op -> RGP : configure scenario\n(simulation.config.json, zones,\nroutes, demand as in project)

Op -> DGP : configure **dataset generation**\n(output / snapshot folder)
DGP -> SCM : set_dataset_output_folder\n(default …/datasets if empty)

Op -> RGP : **Generate Simulation DB**
RGP -> SPW : run preparation (async)
SPW -> DBS : prepare_initial_snapshot()
DBS -> SimDB : build / refresh DB + config hash
SimDB --> SPW : ready
SPW --> RGP : success (Run enabled)

Op -> DGP : **Run simulation**
DGP -> MW : emit run_simulation_clicked\n(project, sumocfg, output_folder)
MW -> SimP : construct SimulationPage
SimP -> SCM : read sumocfg / paths
SimP -> NP : load network
SimP -> SV : display map for TraCI run

@enduml
